 four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CI8CEM2rARgBIhMIwZH11rfrkwMV60XyAB1JCwWASOXMspKYjqXOIMoBBOVVPcU=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqblQ5eURKNHdneTRTRXlGeG5SOS0teFZndERiZ3xBQ3Jtc0treV93WmdmNkZKWTl5YXdCa3lwaTVDSzN1RjZwYUhaRUx2Rm9GQ2l4UjJkSWIxdzBuMUtnd1VmQXBTWG4xOFE1WGw0WUVNbXhPUng3WEhwVGlwazZXU1ExY2hwWWlYLUNadTRMaGtjQ0dacGVIUmZudw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=IJyUcYJMpmU","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqblQ5eURKNHdneTRTRXlGeG5SOS0teFZndERiZ3xBQ3Jtc0treV93WmdmNkZKWTl5YXdCa3lwaTVDSzN1RjZwYUhaRUx2Rm9GQ2l4UjJkSWIxdzBuMUtnd1VmQXBTWG4xOFE1WGw0WUVNbXhPUng3WEhwVGlwazZXU1ExY2hwWWlYLUNadTRMaGtjQ0dacGVIUmZudw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=IJyUcYJMpmU","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CI8CEM2rARgBIhMIwZH11rfrkwMV60XyAB1JCwWASOXMspKYjqXOIMoBBOVVPcU=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbFp1MFdFSGRQcWxINS1DUGNLdk5ZSXVqNFNNZ3xBQ3Jtc0tsNTJxZlR2RTQ0VUh3UDhVcE8xdThiazROcXZxZFlEd3VpakNRZDNzU2F5S0dTTmhlRlJGNlhhNmFKbUlveEdpXzRmVFFJNGJMS29aRWV2V3VsdVQwTHNCMEgyeEhuQUl3S3BEZW10VUxSNlBscEltNA\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2