ruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwjBkfXWt-uTAxXrRfIAHUkLBYBI5cyykpiOpc4gygEE5VU9xQ==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbnpyQUk4RUdBS2JyQUpTSVdKWjh3cE5ERlY4d3xBQ3Jtc0tsaXlNSmVNQl9MRVRIR2FiT0NnTk11Qy01Vy1BTkdwTTh3ZjluVVk2VDhndjB6RHE1RFJVTWphUTRiMWtkTVJoNm53S3RxbC05ZlJsU1YxenlfRVphaXJGN1prMVo4S05yWk9yUHk1RDY1YWV2QmJvSQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=IJyUcYJMpmU","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbnpyQUk4RUdBS2JyQUpTSVdKWjh3cE5ERlY4d3xBQ3Jtc0tsaXlNSmVNQl9MRVRIR2FiT0NnTk11Qy01Vy1BTkdwTTh3ZjluVVk2VDhndjB6RHE1RFJVTWphUTRiMWtkTVJoNm53S3RxbC05ZlJsU1YxenlfRVphaXJGN1prMVo4S05yWk9yUHk1RDY1YWV2QmJvSQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=IJyUcYJMpmU","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwjBkfXWt-uTAxXrRfIAHUkLBYBI5cyykpiOpc4gygEE5VU9xQ==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbmdNOUVzcnhmZXZ4aWkwbVhYNVB0aTVQZWFmd3xBQ3Jtc0ttVFFCYm1DUzQ2RlhKaHg2X09pR2h0RF9mb25ELXhfbGxwQ29mT1JWd3lLS1NIVkRWZkdYM0o4Zk45RG91NFlsZmJlbUh1WHp5NVZDdGFpeURSUXFNS292TmVKVklOa3dfTkhFTTF0OWkwejFfUG9UYw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fcgi-bin%2Fwebscr%3Fcmd%3D_s-xcli